				<td colspan="2"><span>I've pulled agro with my EoE with 125 fire dd and SoE with 150 poison dd and WA 3 from my tank with WA5 Bloodfrenzy (a 155% proc rate weapon - pretty much the finest 1h agro weapon there is before Time) &amp; BoC both with Anger 3 augs...not often or for long, but I have pulled the agro.  When he uses his BoWar with Anger 3 it is much more likely.  This usually only happens in the first few seconds after a pull, but if he has a sucktastic proc rate by bad luck I can force him to taunt several times.
<br />

<br />
Warriors without Anger 3 augs are gimps, at least in my opinion.
