				<td colspan="2"><span>Old song, not worth memming most times.  And nearly worthless once you have fading memories.  I can count the time's I've used it on one hand, and that includes the &quot;Ooh, new song&quot; test run.
<br />

<br />
190 hate = 190 damage, or roughly 2 swings of a wep for an EP geared bard (if not less).  Cast time  is 3 secs, like all else.  So all it does is slow your aggro creation, not halt it.  
<br />

<br />
Granted at level 51 with a so-so tank, it might be worth while.  Although, since it is a detrimental song, I suppose you could pull with it.  Not sure how well it would work, since you cant have negative aggro, but it would ensure a solid tag.
<br />

<br />
Rappa
<br />

